itemDescription: Professor of Ophthalmology and Consultant Ophthalmologist

wikipedia_page.main: Philip I. Murray FRCP, FRCS, FRCOphth is Professor of Ophthalmology at the University of Birmingham, in England, and Honorary Consultant Ophthalmologist at the Birmingham and Midland Eye Centre.
